title: Tiny Desk Contest Top Shelf 2023: Episode 3
description:
NPR Music received nearly 6,000 submissions to this year's Tiny Desk Contest, our annual search for the next great undiscovered artist to play a Tiny Desk concert. Before we reveal this year's winner, our Contest judges are sharing their favorite entries as part of our annual Tiny Desk Contest Top Shelf livestream series. Set your reminder now to join Tiny Desk alums Sudan Archives and Baby Rose as they share their favorites with Tiny Desk series producer Bobby Carter on Thursday, May 4 at 3 p.m. ET.

Learn more about the Contest: https://npr.org/tinydeskcontest
